title: Kim Kardashian supports Landon Rasmussen's mother | Daily Mail Online
text: 'Please pray for this family': Kim Kardashian supports Texas mother whose eight-month-old son died after 'nearly drowning while in the care of a babysitter' Landon Rasmussen died Sunday after being found unresponsive in Killeen, Texas His mother Destiny said Landon's babysitter left him unattended in the bathtub The little boy was found unresponsive ; rescuers managed to revive him But Landon died in his mother's arms almost three weeks later in the hospital Kim Kardashian shared a link to the family's Go Fund Me early Thursday saying Landon's story was breaking her heart
